'''Konohanachiru-hime''' is a Japanese goddess<ref name="Herbert-2010" />{{rp|277-278}}.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Konohanachiruhime • . A History . . of Japan . 日本歴史 |url=https://historyofjapan.co.uk/wiki/konohanachiruhime/ |access-date=2023-11-14 |website=. A History . . of Japan . 日本歴史 |language=en-GB}}</ref>

Her name means "Blossoms-of- the-Trees-Falling-Princess".<ref>{{Cite book |last1=Coulter |first1=Charles Russell |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QEJUEAAAQBAJ&dq=Konohanachiruhime&pg=PA510 |title=Encyclopedia of Ancient Deities |last2=Turner |first2=Patricia |date=2021-12-06 |publisher=McFarland |isbn=978-0-7864-9179-7 |language=en}}</ref>

